g.text: Asks to postpone an entry on Agenda
Shows the tasks of the Agenda and asks to
select the task to be postponed
show the popup to select a new execution date,
asks to type the required data (new execution date, start hour and start minute)
for all tasks in agenda get
if team and vehicles are all available in the
work period of the new task continue
[for every vehicle in vehicles assigned to task]
